Firmware and Software Security Update Period
In accordance with the requirements of The Product Security and Telecommunications Infrastructure (Security Requirements for Relevant Connectable Products) Regulations 2023 (U.K. 2023 No. 1007), Celestron declares the following regarding support for its products:
Hardware/Software Eligible for Support:
Celestron hardware that is capable of receiving security updates.
Software that is capable of receiving security updates that is pre-installed on a Celestron product when the product is supplied to a customer.
Software that is capable of receiving security updates that must be installed on the product for all Celestron’s intended purposes of the product that use that hardware.
Software that is pre-installed in a Celestron product when the product is supplied to a customer or software that is installable in that product.
LIMITED LIFETIME WARRANTY
THIS LIMITED WARRANTY GIVES YOU SPECIFIC LEGAL RIGHTS AND YOU MAY ALSO HAVE OTHER RIGHTS, WHICH VARY FROM STATE TO STATE. THE LIMITED WARRANTY CAN ALSO BE FOUND ONLINE AT WWW.CELESTRON.COM/PAGES/WARRANTY.
CELESTRON WARRANTS YOUR PRODUCT TO BE FREE FROM DEFECTS IN MATERIALS AND WORKMANSHIP FOR THE USEFUL LIFE OF THE PRODUCT FOR THE ORIGINAL OWNER. CELESTRON WILL REPAIR OR REPLACE PRODUCTS OR PARTS THEREOF WHICH, UPON INSPECTION BY CELESTRON, ARE FOUND TO BE DEFECTIVE IN MATERIALS OR WORKMANSHIP.
CELESTRON LIMITS THE DURATION AND REMEDIES OF ALL IMPLIED WARRANTIES, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION THE WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE TO THE DURATION OF THIS EXPRESS LIMITED WARRANTY.
